Sentencas: Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3(SSC)-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3(LSGMC5) composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells were prepared using wet-chemistry method.

Sentencas: The SSC powders were prepared using the glycine-nitrate method and the LSGMC5 powders were synthesized using the citrate method.

Sentencas: The XRD pattern of SSC powders calcined at temperatures higher than 1223 K corresponded to a desired perovskite structure.
